Comex silver futures held sharplyhigher morning levels at midday, but further advances werechecked by overseas and commercial selling.    May was up 12.5 cents at 6.705 dlrs as of 1223 hrs EDT.July was up 13.1 cents at 6.785 dlrs, both exactly as they wereat 1000 hrs EDT this morning.    Traders said locals remain long and speculative interestcontinues. But profit taking has intensified on expectations ofa corrective downward move if the market becomes overbought.    Some interest has been drawn away from silver by a furtherrecord-setting stock market advance. Reuter&#3;